metadata.description: Purchase whitelist access to mint in the up and coming project from KAI. NON-TRANSFERABLE.CLAY_ is a fully on-chain 3D generative art project. The first of it's kind. The perfect shape is within us, we are sculpted, we are clay.A project that pushes boundaries. Combining innovations in computer graphics and the web3 space, it is a project like no other.
